    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本游戏的操作非常独特，建议在体验之前先观看页面顶部的操作指南视频</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款第三人称视角的扫雷游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >标记全部地雷是每一关的任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/f82871d31ef4fea4911a3ac9e6443fd6.poster.avif?t=1752886330\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/f82871d31ef4fea4911a3ac9e6443fd6.webm?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/f82871d31ef4fea4911a3ac9e6443fd6.mp4?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雷区可能被障碍物覆盖，可以爆破清除。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/fede7ace89218bae13bbdb3004d76462.poster.avif?t=1752886330\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/fede7ace89218bae13bbdb3004d76462.webm?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/fede7ace89218bae13bbdb3004d76462.mp4?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在关卡中，您将遭遇阻止您行动的守卫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您拥有丰富的技能来对抗他们，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近身的格斗是您的基本技能，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/20439928ce3bf00d016f9f20dc29dcab.poster.avif?t=1752886330\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/20439928ce3bf00d016f9f20dc29dcab.webm?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/20439928ce3bf00d016f9f20dc29dcab.mp4?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >闪电是中远程打击单个目标的好办法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/70f1824fb6ccfde022fcf2a78dc1c887.poster.avif?t=1752886330\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/70f1824fb6ccfde022fcf2a78dc1c887.webm?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/70f1824fb6ccfde022fcf2a78dc1c887.mp4?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对付多个目标可以使用冲击波。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/f48d7840753e783450629c076219edc1.poster.avif?t=1752886330\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/f48d7840753e783450629c076219edc1.webm?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/f48d7840753e783450629c076219edc1.mp4?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狙击瞄准有时候也是必要的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/372f00f7cfdf1a4badfe78ae8be0876e.poster.avif?t=1752886330\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/372f00f7cfdf1a4badfe78ae8be0876e.webm?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/372f00f7cfdf1a4badfe78ae8be0876e.mp4?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是的，您甚至可以飞行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多的技能，欢迎您进入游戏后亲自体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款致敬扫雷、炸弹人、俄罗斯方块的游戏，请相信，您值得拥有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/b70c18bae115e5d87df762f576abfa6c.poster.avif?t=1752886330\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/b70c18bae115e5d87df762f576abfa6c.webm?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/b70c18bae115e5d87df762f576abfa6c.mp4?t=1752886330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
